            <title>[HBASE-9527] Review all old api that takes a table name as a byte array and ensure none can pass ns + tablename</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-9527</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Go over all old APIs that take a table name and ensure that it is not possible to pass in a byte array that is a namespace + tablename; instead throw an exception.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
